DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to determine the pharmacokinetic (PK) parameters of vortioxetine after single and multiple oral dosing to healthy Chinese men and women.
DOC.brief_title: Pharmacokinetic Properties of Vortioxetine in Healthy Young Chinese Men and Women
